sub_title: Head of Political Affairs at the Embassy of the Kingdom of The Netherlands
summary: Currently working as Head of Political Affairs at the Embassy of the Kingdom of The Netherlands in London. Background: Economist (MSc), consultant at the World bank (2002-2003) and JPO with FAO in South Sudan (2003-2005), worked as deputy Head of the Trade Politics Unit at the Ministry of Foreign Affairs in the Netherlands. Furthermore: Trade Promotion and capacity building (in the energy sector in Tanzania and Mozambique), International relations (Security Department), experience with politics (private secretary to the Minister of Development Cooperation and candidate member of parliament).
